__NOTOC__
{{Client function}}

==Syntax== 
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
bool isCapsLockEnabled()
</syntaxhighlight> 

===Returns===
Returns ''true'' if caps lock is toggled (on), ''false'' otherwise.

==Example== 
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">function checkCaps()
    iprint(isCapsLockEnabled(), getTickCount())
end
addCommandHandler("caps", checkCaps)</syntaxhighlight>

==Requirements==
{{Requirements|n/a|1.5.9-9.21313|}}

